In pcbnew:
Plot silk, mask and copper layers to SVG format with "Exclude PCB edges" options unchecked to the project folder.
Place origin point at the upper left corner and create drill file with options: units "mm", format "Gerber", "Mirror y axis", drill origin "Auxiliary axis".

Convert SVG to diffuse texture and normal map:
./rasterizer.py -i ~/Documents/kicad/lpc13xx/ -p lpc13xx --mask 38,104,68
Generate board model and save VRML file:
./b2m.py -i ~/Documents/kicad/lpc13xx/ -p lpc13xx --mask 38,104,68
Show 3D model:
./wrload.py -v ~/Documents/kicad/lpc13xx/board.wrl